  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>魔剣エターナルソード！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The Demonic Eternal Sword?!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>25</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>そう。
生け贄に捧げた命と同数の
新しい命を生み出す、まさに奇跡の剣</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's right. A truly miraculous sword,
which gives birth to new life equal to the
number of lives offered to it as sacrifices.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>34</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>それが今のエターナルソードなのです</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That is the Eternal Sword now.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>34</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>どっちみち危険だって事に変わりはねぇ。
だったらやる事も変えるつもりはねぇよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Either way, doesn't change the fact that
it's dangerous. In which case, I have no
plans to change what I'm about to do here.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>24</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ユーリ。
エターナルソードの力を使えば
あなたの罪も許されるのですよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yuri. If you use the power of the
Eternal Sword, your sins will be forgiven.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>34</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>あなたを認めない、
あなたを罰しようとする人間をすべて
消し去ってしまえばいいのですから</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You could erase all those who do not
accept you and would punish you.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>34</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>言いたい事はそれだけか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Is that all you're gonna say?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>24</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>……なんですって？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...What did you say?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>34</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>悪いが、戯れ言に付き合う趣味はねぇんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Sorry to say, but I'm not interested in your jokes.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>24</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>それに気分も悪い。
気に入らねぇんだよ、てめぇの考え方……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Not to mention, you make me sick.
I can't stand the way you think...!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>24</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
